HEADWORD: Aquarelle
<hw>Aq`ua*relle"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
Ital <ets>acquerello</ets>, fr. <ets>acqua</ets> water, L.
<ets>aqua</ets>.]</ety> <def>A design or painting in thin transparent
water colors; also, the mode of painting in such colors.</def>⟦br⟧
